<div class="tabs-content" data-tabs-content="animal-tabs">
  <div class="tabs-panel is-active" id="health">
    <div class="callout success" style="margin-bottom: 1%;">
      <p> Animal health is a very important issue and needs to be handled with care.
        Ensure  you always record every activity and the records are correct.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 1%;">
      <div class="medium-6 columns medium-offset-4" style="margin-top:2%" align="center">
